data.name: Chickpea and Spinach Curry
data.quickTastyDescription: A hearty and nutritious curry packed with protein and greens, perfect for a quick meal.
detailedCookingInstructions: Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.
Add chopped onion and minced garlic, cooking until onion is translucent, about 5 minutes.
Stir in curry powder and cook for another minute until fragrant.
Add the canned chickpeas (drained and rinsed) and coconut milk, stirring well to combine.
Bring to a simmer and let cook for about 10 minutes.
Add the fresh spinach and cook until wilted, about 2-3 minutes more.
Season with salt to taste and serve hot.
